OL,7,FAndrew Rowlands, from County Durham,
OL,8,Fwas 18 when he was killed in a car
OL,9,Fcrash in June 2020. He had gone to fix
OL,10,Fa car for friends, but the car had
OL,11,Fbeen bought for #100 the night before
OL,12,Fand was illegal and unroadworthy. The
OL,13,Fdriver of the car was 17 and had no
OL,14,Flicence.
OL,16,FAndrew was travelling as a passenger
OL,17,Fwhen the car crashed and he died from
OL,18,Fhis injuries.
