OL,4,Cdriver licences to avoid more road
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FHis mum, Karen Rowlands, told ITV Tyne
OL,8,FTees: "We've lost everything. We lost
OL,9,Four future. Our life just ended the
OL,10,Fday we lost Andrew, but there are kids
OL,11,Fout there who are still living and we
OL,12,Fhave to protect those kids. We have to
OL,13,Fgive them their future."
OL,15,FMrs Rowlands and her husband, John,
OL,16,Fhave joined a group of bereaved
OL,17,Fparents called the Forget Me Not
OL,18,FFamilies United group in calling on
OL,19,Fthe government to introduce graduated
OL,20,Fdriver licences for all newly
OL,21,Fqualified drivers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
