OL,7,FIt would mean the new young drivers
OL,8,Fwould be prohibited from travelling
OL,9,Fwith peer passengers for the first six
OL,10,Fmonths after their test.
OL,12,F"A car is a dangerous thing," Mr
OL,13,FRowlands said. "Get used to it, get
OL,14,Fconfident with it, before you fill it
OL,15,Fwith your friends on a weekend,
OL,16,Fbecause there are so many distractions.
