OL,7,F"You could have a car full of your
OL,8,Ffriends in and there could be a bit of
OL,9,Fmusic on in the background, they could
OL,10,Fbe talking to each other, and you're
OL,11,Fkind of earwigging and stuff and bang,
OL,12,Fbefore you know it, you're in a
OL,13,Fserious situation.
