OL,7,F"I don't believe it's mandatory to put
OL,8,Fa P plate on your car. It's an option.
OL,9,FMaybe something like that would be
OL,10,Flooked at, that is mandatory, you've
OL,11,Fgot to have the P plate on and if I'm
OL,12,Fseen carrying a car full of passengers
OL,13,Fand my car has got a P plate on it,
OL,14,Fthen all of a sudden that is going to
OL,15,Fpreempt the police to pull me over.
OL,17,F"And I don't want to lose my licence
OL,18,Fif I've just got it. So simple things
OL,19,Flike that, there's lots of options,
OL,20,Fbut start having the conversation
OL,21,Freally, that's all we need to do."
