OL,7,FOne in five young drivers have crashed
OL,8,Fwithin a year of passing their test,
OL,9,Faccording to the latest data and more
OL,10,Fthan 1,500 young drivers are killed or
OL,11,Fseriously injured each year.JThe AA's
OL,12,Fresearch found 72% of people agree
OL,13,Fwith the introduction of Graduated
OL,14,FDriver Licences for new drivers, while
OL,15,F76% would like to introduce eye tests
OL,16,Ffor drivers over 70.
OL,18,FPresident of the AA, Edmund King said:
OL,19,F"Every driver needs experience and
OL,20,Fjust after you've passed your test,
OL,21,Fyou haven't got that experience.
