OL,7,F"So actually waiting another six
OL,8,Fmonths before you can have same age
OL,9,Fpassengers isn't really too much to
OL,10,Fask and it will keep many young people
OL,11,Falive.
OL,13,F"There are far too many crashes we
OL,14,Fhear about with four or five teenagers
OL,15,Fin the car, it is really tragic and
OL,16,Fthere is something we can do to
OL,17,Fcounter this."
