OL,7,FA government spokesperson said: "While
OL,8,Fthe UK has some of the safest roads in
OL,9,Fthe world, any death is a tragedy
OL,10,Fwhich is why we continue working
OL,11,Ftirelessly to improve road safety for
OL,12,Feveryone.
OL,14,F"Our THINK! campaign is specifically
OL,15,Ftargeted at young male drivers, and we
OL,16,Fhave commissioned research designed to
OL,17,Fhelp learner and newly-qualified
OL,18,Fdrivers improve their skills and
OL,19,Fsafety."
